creator: Pogo Technologies Inc
descriptionHtml:
Earn rewards and savings on every purchase. Automatically fetch rewards without the hassle of receipt scanning.

Pogo turns your everyday purchases into automatic savings and rewards. The best part: you never have to take photos of a receipt again. With the Pogo mobile app, you simply link your existing debit and credit cards and Pogo automatically fetches your receipt for you. So every time you go grocery shopping, shop online, or pay for utilities, you can get rewards with the click of a button. It's the easiest way to save on everything you buy. Here's how:

1. Link your existing credit and debit cards (2-factor verification, 256-bit encryption)
2. Pogo automatically requests your receipts from retailers
3. Earn points on every purchase you make
4. Receive personalized cash back at places you shop and take high-paying surveys
5. Cash Out

There is so much that makes Pogo different and easier than other savings apps. Unlike other receipt apps, you never have to take photos of receipts. Pogo takes care of getting your receipt automatically through our unique technology. No more un-wrinkling or finding the lighting and never have receipts rejected again. Unlike other cash back and rebate apps, you never have to select a coupon or offer with Pogo. Pogo simply gives your rewards on EVERY purchase – WITHOUT receipt scanning or receipt photos. It's simply the best way to save points on every day purchases. We fetch the best rewards for you.

Pogo rewards you EVERY TIME you shop - any store, any brand, online or in-store:

- Grocery stores
- Restaurants and Bars
- Online Shopping
- Gas & Cars
- Utilities
- Phone Bills
- And more...

We also have other money-saving rewards and earnings features that you can enjoy. You can earn bonus rewards and savings for answering surveys about the places you shop and products you buy. You receive personalized cash back offers and rebates at places you shop. In fact, we have over 15,000 businesses where you receive personalized rewards and savings from. With information on where you shop and what you buy, we fetch rewards for you automatically. Never fetch rewards again – with Pogo, rewards come to you!

On top of all of that, Pogo is transparent with how data is being used. In fact, Pogo pays you Data Dividends, which is 10% of the money that we make whenever your data is used. It's your data - you deserve to know how it's being used and get paid for it!

Earn real cash / money / dough (did you know they call it "dosh" in England?). With Pogo, you can cash out via Venmo or PayPal fast and easy as soon as you've reached $3 in savings. No more high cash out minimums like other cash back or receipt apps. When you earn a reward, you deserve to fetch it.

No more receipt scanning, clipping coupons, chasing down expiring deals or missing out on savings. Just shop and automatically earn points for all your purchases and automatic receipts. It's time to say bye to receipt photos, and hello to Pogo rewards. The best money-saving app out there.

title: Pogo: Receipt-Free Rewards on Every Purchase

creator: Pogo Technologies Inc
descriptionHtml:
Earn rewards and savings on every purchase. Automatically fetch rewards without the hassle of receipt scanning.

Pogo turns your everyday purchases into automatic savings and rewards. The best part: you never have to take photos of a receipt again. With the Pogo mobile app, you simply link your existing debit and credit cards and Pogo automatically fetches your receipt for you. So every time you go grocery shopping, shop online, or pay for utilities, you can get rewards with the click of a button. It's the easiest way to save on everything you buy. Here's how:

1. Link your existing credit and debit cards (2-factor verification, 256-bit encryption)
2. Pogo automatically requests your receipts from retailers
3. Earn points on every purchase you make
4. Receive personalized cash back at places you shop and take high-paying surveys
5. Cash Out

There is so much that makes Pogo different and easier than other savings apps. Unlike other receipt apps, you never have to take photos of receipts. Pogo takes care of getting your receipt automatically through our unique technology. No more un-wrinkling or finding the lighting and never have receipts rejected again. Unlike other cash back and rebate apps, you never have to select a coupon or offer with Pogo. Pogo simply gives your rewards on EVERY purchase – WITHOUT receipt scanning or receipt photos. It's simply the best way to save points on every day purchases. We fetch the best rewards for you.

Pogo rewards you EVERY TIME you shop - any store, any brand, online or in-store:

- Grocery stores
- Restaurants and Bars
- Online Shopping
- Gas & Cars
- Utilities
- Phone Bills
- And more...

We also have other money-saving rewards and earnings features that you can enjoy. You can earn bonus rewards and savings for answering surveys about the places you shop and products you buy. You receive personalized cash back offers and rebates at places you shop. In fact, we have over 15,000 businesses where you receive personalized rewards and savings from. With information on where you shop and what you buy, we fetch rewards for you automatically. Never fetch rewards again – with Pogo, rewards come to you!

On top of all of that, Pogo is transparent with how data is being used. In fact, Pogo pays you Data Dividends, which is 10% of the money that we make whenever your data is used. It's your data - you deserve to know how it's being used and get paid for it!

Earn real cash / money / dough (did you know they call it "dosh" in England?). With Pogo, you can cash out via Venmo or PayPal fast and easy as soon as you've reached $3 in savings. No more high cash out minimums like other cash back or receipt apps. When you earn a reward, you deserve to fetch it.

No more receipt scanning, clipping coupons, chasing down expiring deals or missing out on savings. Just shop and automatically earn points for all your purchases and automatic receipts. It's time to say bye to receipt photos, and hello to Pogo rewards. The best money-saving app out there.

descriptionHtml:
Earn rewards and savings on every purchase, automatically find more ways to save on your finances, and get paid for sharing more data (if you choose!).

Pogo is your agent in today’s digital world, always working to bring you more money and control:

1. Sync your data with the app, such as transactions, shopping history, and location.
2. Get rewards on every single purchase you make - from groceries and restaurants to online shopping and bills.
3. Find automatic savings on everything in your life - including lower rates on insurance and refunds on bank fees.
4. Get paid for your data - if you choose. You own your data, and we believe opt-in should be the default. Whether it’s for anonymous market research, surveys or personalized marketing, you can earn extra cash whenever you choose.

There is so much that makes Pogo easier than other savings apps. Connect your data, and we’ll do the work for you. No more searching for savings, taking photos of receipts, or clipping coupons. The Pogo app is simply the best way to save on everything in your life. Never fetch rewards again – with Pogo, savings come to you!

Turn all your rewards and savings into real cash. With Pogo, you can cash out via Venmo or PayPal fast and easy. No more high cash out minimums like other apps. Start saving $$$ with Pogo today!

Your phone's turned into your side hustle. With Pogo, playing games, scanning receipts, and filling out surveys all add up to cash rewards and savings. It’s the smart way to blend entertainment with earning, turning your everyday actions into financial gains.

Speak Up, Cash In: Got opinions? We’ve got rewards for them. Dive into our paid surveys and let your voice earn you cash. It’s straightforward: answer, earn, and grow your savings.

Profit Without the Sweat: Forget the old hustle of coupon clipping and online deal hunting. A quick setup with our app brings savings and earnings straight into your life, effortlessly. It’s transforming every tap, every purchase, and every play into opportunities for financial growth. How? Just connect your bank account and your favorite retailer accounts, that’s it.

Privacy Pays: Sharing data is entirely up to you, but when you do, it pays off. We treat your data with respect and offer rewards for your trust. It’s privacy, with benefits.

Cash Out Made Easy: Long waits to access your earnings are history. With swift transfers to Venmo or PayPal, your money is always ready when you are. It's about making the cash-out process as smooth as your earnings.

Get rewarded for playing games, scanning receipts, and taking surveys. Shop with big names like Walmart, Amazon, and Target and see your savings grow. Make every day count by turning simple tasks into cash. Join us and start earning and saving easily every single day. Download Pogo today.
